title: __**Duos / Trios / 5-Stacks:**__
description:
**1. Duos/Trios** are fine if they are not significantly better or worse than you. This is your review, not theirs. All other VOD review requirements apply.

**2. 5-Stacks** require all teammates to be members of the Discord for at least a week. You will be required to ping them in #stream-chat when your VOD is reviewed. Consult #lf-5stack for help finding a team. All other VOD review requirements apply.
